Isles of Gauznia
Installation Guide

The first (and only) step to ensuring Isles of Gauznia will run
on your machine is to install java.



Linux

Install java runtime environment (jre). Recommended version is
jre7.

  Arch Linux

  # pacman -S jre7-openjdk

Windows

Navigate to the official java website and download the correct
installer for your architecture, depending on if your machine
is 32 or 64-bit. Run through the installer until it tells you
that you have successfully installed java

jre is the only requirement of Isles of Gauznia and no further setup
is needed.
